e="preserve">Touriya Jabrane (– born Saadia Kraytif; 16 October 1952 – 24 August 2020) was a Moroccan theatre director, actress and politician. Between 2007 and 2009, she held the position of Minister of Culture in the cabinet of Abbas El Fassi. She was born in Casablanca.
Jabrane died on 24 August 2020, aged 67.
